Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:31.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:37.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:43.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:49.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:02:06.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:13.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:20.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:25.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:32.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:43.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正当我们到处打探\N奈落的行踪的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上遇见了三只小猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这三只猴子又聒噪又冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些可爱的小猴子\N正在到处寻找的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们负责守护的\N猿神大爷的神体石像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而最后在村子的\N腌菜缸里面找到了猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出了一段\N令人惊讶的一段话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他曾经\N感觉到一股强烈的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝丑寅方向飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了  那一定是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向…\N是指东北方向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子\N已经知道接下来该往哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是丑寅方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第89话 他和他之间的探病大战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明早就该上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果现在是什么状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你别那么任性啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是戈薇自己喜欢感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我又不是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对大家  很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有耽误到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正马上又要开始旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也需要\N一点时间准备准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去打理一些道具才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子戈薇这场病\N来得还真是时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万不要放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶快把病养好怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道你很心急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不要再责怪戈薇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没有责怪她的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果戈薇要安心养病的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好还是避开犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏枫姥姥又不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧得很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要回家休息几天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们那边\N应该有很好的医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说还有各式各样的药呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看我还是回家休养
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛跟我们这么客气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘  我来背你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在打什么主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天还要再请一天病假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次只是小小的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮篱同学今天又请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次好像是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感冒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?没胃口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  我去煮点热饮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你配着药吃下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么久戈薇都没回来过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一回来就感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概那边的天气比较冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得好好休养几天才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的感冒也要请假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她以前\N不是老用一些罕见的病请假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说要不要一起去看她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去探病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇这次既然是感冒\N应该会在家休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要住院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有见到戈薇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真的有点想她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要去日暮同学家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说戈薇突然感冒了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要跟我们一起去…\N是吗?得了感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要不要跟我们去探病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪里怪气的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别乱了方寸  利吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇静一点就可以解决
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实在的\N好久都没打过妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为犬夜叉他们不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要加倍努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快射箭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你碍到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是你啊枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说\N最近有很多妖怪出来作怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子里面的人\N被袭击得怕得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是因为\N奈落突然躲起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前奈落在\N这些妖怪都乖乖的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下还不趁机会出来作乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活得不耐烦啦  死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是特地赶来帮我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他根本没想那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别挡着我  滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子\N知不知道本大爷是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管你是谁都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子今天有事\N一定要进这个泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个泥沼\N已经是我的势力范围了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再敢罗罗唆唆\N我的脑袋会吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用脑袋吃掉我是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事吃吃看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:08:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个山谷\N全都是我的势力范围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个瀑布…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聋了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪一直都没再出现耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底躲到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那边干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来了就顺便嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:09:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在发烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子跟喉咙觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点点咳嗽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的  一点点小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算一点小感冒\N也不能够太大意喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得你最近\N为什么这么常生病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N那个他有没有过来看你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装了  那个像太保的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会来看我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他果然一点也不体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在是什么情况嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你快点医好它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他是住远了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远了一点是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫北条同学来看你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学  你怎么也来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一听说你感冒\N就想要来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过我一直很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:11:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底我能够为你做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想到可以送你\N能够帮助恢复健康的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不嫌弃的话  这些是送你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是可以保佑你\N身体健康的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还其实这些都\N出自于你们家神社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们家的那些护身符\N一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是哑铃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你最好\N多做一点运动锻炼体力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先请进来坐再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇回家养病啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想\N在家里应该比较适合养病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就叫她回去养病了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛不说一声就这样跑回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个浑帐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你把我扔在这里\N一个人跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是名产吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  马上要出远门了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是准备路上吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明记得收在这里头的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到啦找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我们日暮家代代相传
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以治百病的灵丹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算让我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  爷爷\N有了这瓶药
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信过了不久之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇一定可以完全好起来的\N算了  管他的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蚋让开\N太好了…找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  闯出大祸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇好一点了没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐她一直在睡觉耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有好多人来看她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些男生都好大一阵骚动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪亚由美太有魅力了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这些了啦  绘理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们班那些男生\N好像也常在讨论耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些臭男生\N也会在背后说我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我想出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真的追来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么追来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然追到戈薇家来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是  来探病的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好体贴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然他什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇已经\N有男朋友的事都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过听说\N戈薇的男朋友很体贴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在在说的是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢\N我们说的是戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  戈薇\N已经有个在交往的男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  不过连\N戈薇生病都没来看她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很过分的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校…\N大家感觉起来很快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太  什么事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊\N想看看你现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来探我的病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫七宝跟珊瑚\N他们两个紧张兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我还有谁能来看你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是还有一点点在发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身好像也没什么力气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别以为\N我是来带你回去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也认为你应该好好休养
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能回家休养最好不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧  已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学\N你有没有什么烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦恼?你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意当你的忠实听众
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者应该说  我希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什么事\N你都可以跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽我最大的努力帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以换句话说  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们能够交往的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会…啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们猜这题会不会考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要学力测验啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学力测验?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这次考试结果\N是升学的参考指标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有来上课的这段期间\N有没有温书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没温到什么书…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇真受不你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连明天会不会来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我\N出题的范围是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在生病不会想来考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要考了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学  你帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是有什么烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你帮我恶补好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑不撑得住啊这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都没有休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:17:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然科这个部分\N它的范围已经很明确了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要把公式背好就行…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不要死撑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们继续吧  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的很谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们帮了我这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个什么学校考试的\N真有那么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话又说回来  你感冒又没好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个什么鬼考试管他去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为感冒好了要回学校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不用功的话就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先把感冒治好比较要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两样都同样重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说你现在\N赶快乖乖上床睡觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很想回学校嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出去啦\N不要妨碍我温书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  现在觉得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈煮了一点稀饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃一点好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每样看起来都好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个拿到外面去卖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以赚不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你们两个最好不要乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没拿\N什么都没碰过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  头痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥你不是走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想借用一下你们家的炉灶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炉灶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用瓦斯炉行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要补充营养就得靠\N肝脏  肝脏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮子肝  鲤鱼肝  鸡肝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上做药引用的草还有树根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥\N你要吃这些东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  这是药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点喝下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝下去包管你百病全消
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么感冒一定马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是保证功效如神喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个药是你自己熬的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能够治得好病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种怪味道我还能够忍受啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这个药真的有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿  咿…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐把肝脏汤喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝脏汤…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶  好像真的有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没骗你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没什么大不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你居然还知道\N这种配药处方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我老妈教的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈做给你吃过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  材料有点不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老妈用的\N是放了很久的干货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用的是生鲜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生鲜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生鲜的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生鲜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总…总之效果很棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟你说不需要那么客气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也赶快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你念的是不是什么咒语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是\N很久以前我老妈教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身都舒服多了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你的药很有效喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.41,0:22:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就跟你说过会有效的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然好多了\N那我就可以去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要考试我也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候出门\N一定会迟到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕连考试都赶不上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走  一定来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你叫我快一点也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.43,0:22:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想要赶上考试的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感冒已经好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的睡了一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在好像全都好了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试准备得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我尽全力就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:39.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:48.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:58.20,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:08.20,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.70,0:24:13.12,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:18.02,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:25.45,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.32,0:24:32.00,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.00,0:24:36.17,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.57,0:24:43.47,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.92,0:24:53.47,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.65,0:25:00.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.49,0:25:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.13,0:25:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你一个男人之间的重大秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.50,0:25:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.46,0:25:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么是恋爱\N噗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.93,0:25:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱就是永远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.20,0:25:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛无缘无故问我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我偷偷喜欢上小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.77,0:25:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  这件事让你去解决
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.74,0:25:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个可爱的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.27,0:25:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么样都会想出办法来的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.24,0:25:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉\N草太大胆的爱情告白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.78,0:25:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个问题\N简直比打妖怪还要棘手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.40,0:25:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
