Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:26:39.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,性格非常沉稳\N但是成绩却相当不错{\pos(255,438)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:26:40.80,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,步美{\pos(442,186)}
